text: The Free Democratic Party (, FDP; , PLD), also called Radical Democratic Party (, PRD; , PLR) was a liberal political party in Switzerland. The FDP was founded in 1894. On 1 January 2009, it merged with the Liberal Party of Switzerland to become the FDP. The Liberals.
